title: Didn's Come with a Key; 0-0-0 Didn't work to Unlock
body: Overall the product looks good. It's lightweight, feels tough. However, there is no extra zipper to expand when u need. It also didn't come with a key. Moreover, we spend significant amount of time to figure what's the default number to unlock. When googled, it said 0-0-0 and the initial default key; whereas after good amount of time and energy to try out, it opened with 5-5-5. This is not a good customer experience.
